            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#静脉曲张的四大危险因素#】①久站、久坐；②负重；③穿高跟鞋；④跷二郎腿。#两个动作预防静脉曲张#：①找个平稳的位置坐下，把腿抬平，将脚尖、脚掌向...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%9D%99%E8%84%89%E6%9B%B2%E5%BC%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%9D%99%E8%84%89%E6%9B%B2%E5%BC%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#静脉曲张的四大危险因素#</span></a>】①久站、久坐；②负重；③穿高跟鞋；④跷二郎腿。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E9%9D%99%E8%84%89%E6%9B%B2%E5%BC%A0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E9%9D%99%E8%84%89%E6%9B%B2%E5%BC%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#两个动作预防静脉曲张#</span></a>：①找个平稳的位置坐下，把腿抬平，将脚尖、脚掌向下踩，再将脚尖、脚掌向上勾，每次停顿3-5秒，连续做5组。②把鞋子脱掉，把脚踝搁在膝盖上，用手从脚踝向膝盖方向一点一点地捏动小腿肌肉，用力要均匀👇🏻（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6lHOd7y" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
